1)	Take 1 Server-PT, 3 PC, 1 Wireless Router (WRT300N)
2)	Use Copper Straight-Through cable
Server (FastEthernet0) --- Wireless Router (Ethernet 1)

3)	Click on Server  Desktop  IP Configuration
Select DHCP
Add IP Address as label

4)	Click on PC (for every PCs)
Turn OFF
Remove the bottom part
Add the right bottom part
Turn ON

5)	Check Connection. Click on any PC  Desktop  Command Prompt
ping 192.168.0.100
Desktop  Web Browser
192.168.0.100

Click on Server  Desktop  IPv4 Firewall
Turn ON

Action: Deny
Protocol: ICMP
Remote IP: 0.0.0.0
Remote Wildcard Mask: 255.255.255.255
Click on Add

Action: Allow
Protocol: IP
Remote IP: 0.0.0.0
Remote Wildcard Mask: 255.255.255.255
Click on Add

6)	Check Connection. Click on any PC  Desktop  Command Prompt
ping 192.168.0.100
Desktop  Web Browser
192.168.0.100



 
